text: Alejandra Müller Arrieta (born October 29, 1997, in Mexico City, Mexico), known as Ale Müller, is a Mexican actress and singer who first gained popularity for her debut role as Clara Licona in the Mexican sitcom La CQ."Ale Müller enfrenta a las momias", El Siglo de Durango, October 30, 2014. Retrieved July 18, 2015 She also voiced Valentina Luis in the film La leyenda de las momias de Guanajuato, and performed on stage in Santa Claus y la carta misteriosa.
